prompts.frontCover:
A flat 2D botanical illustration style greeting card front. In the center, there is a cartoon illustration of a happy couple, Lao Lao and Jordan, who highly resemble the people in the reference photo.

Lao Lao, on the left, is an East Asian woman with long, straight dark brown hair. She is smiling, wearing thin gold-rimmed glasses, a light blue crewneck sweatshirt (with no logos or text), and black pants. Her arms are crossed in front of her.

Jordan, on the right, is a young man of Southeast Asian descent with short, textured dark hair. He is standing slightly behind Lao Lao, hugging her from behind with his arms wrapped around her waist. He has a big, warm smile and is wearing a tan/brown hoodie (with no logos or text) and dark reddish-brown pants.

They are playfully struggling over a giant, comically oversized birthday cupcake with bright pink frosting and a single lit candle on top, holding it between them. Lao Lao is trying to pull it towards herself with a mischievous grin, while Jordan is playfully trying to pull it back, laughing.

The couple is framed by an elegant, asymmetrical wreath of detailed botanical elements. This includes lush monstera leaves, delicate fern fronds, eucalyptus branches, and vibrant, blooming pink peonies and white anemones, all rendered in soft, organic watercolor textures.

In the center of the card, slightly overlapping the botanical wreath at the top, is the text "Happy Birthday to my favorite human bean" in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script. The text is colored a deep charcoal gray. The background is a solid, soft cream color.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
prompts.backCover: A minimalist flat 2D botanical illustration for a greeting card back cover. The background is a solid, soft cream color. In the top-left corner, there is a single, small, elegant cluster of botanical elements: one delicate pink peony blossom and a sprig of eucalyptus leaves, rendered in a soft, organic watercolor texture. The design is very minimal, occupying only the top-left portion of the card, leaving the rest of the space, especially the bottom-right corner, completely empty. The style is clean and elegant.
prompts.leftInterior: A flat 2D botanical illustration for the left interior panel of a greeting card. The background is a solid, soft cream color. An elegant, asymmetrical floral border cascades down the left side of the panel, from the top-left corner towards the bottom-left. The arrangement features a tasteful mix of monstera leaves, delicate fern fronds, and eucalyptus branches, with accents of pink peonies and white anemones. The composition is rendered in soft watercolor textures and is designed to be a beautiful, decorative element that complements the front cover without being overwhelming, leaving the majority of the panel clean and open.
prompts.rightInterior:
A flat 2D illustration for the right interior panel of a greeting card, designed to hold a written message. The background is a solid, soft cream color, creating a large, open space for text. In the bottom-right corner, there is a very small and simple botanical accent: a single sprig with a few eucalyptus leaves and one small, unopened pink peony bud. The illustration is rendered in a soft watercolor style and is placed discreetly to add a touch of elegance without distracting from the message area.

Display this exact text in elegant, clearly readable handwritten script: "To my dearest Lao Lao,

Happy Birthday! I was going to get you a fancy, expensive gift, but then I remembered you already have me. You're welcome! I hope your day is as amazing as you are, and that you get at least one thing you actually wanted.

With all my love,
Jordan"
